data.title: This is not a restaurant.
data.text:
E A Sween is the corporate location and commissary for the Deli Express Sandwich lines which are sold in many convenience stores. They do not serve any food here, they make it here , and deliver their sandwiches via trucks to their customers. Please ignore the ratings and other information shown here because this review would not publish unless I filled out all the boxes. 
THERE IS NO DINING HERE.
